    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This power unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system to deliver a sharp, linear induction note all the way to its 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring across the rear axle. This example has been properly maintained, with recent attention paid to the rod bearings and throttle actuators to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis retains its factory-spec lateral stiffness, providing communicative feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the mechanical components\u2014including the subframe bushings and damping rates\u2014remain in excellent working order. A purist-spec performance machine for those who prioritize powertrain integrity and analog engagement.",
